RoleType.description:
Affects how an image is placed.

Also known as “weighting” in Composer, but we respect the CAPI naming.

position.description:
position is an index starting at 1 for all the images in an
article, including main media.

It is generated by `addImageIDs`

lightbox.description:
We store a copy of the caption and credit for an image in the
lightbox property because some article types expect the caption
and credit to be deleted.

A better, more semantic, solution would be to keep caption and
credit defined but refactor <Caption /> to not display them
depending on `format.design`. If you did that refactor you could
remove this property
